reviewText: the dvd kept jumping colors so much that  it was hard to watch along with the static on it this was not good at all.  the info was clearly narrated but could not keep watching it
An excellent find thanks to a YouTube excerpt I happened upon luckily. This is a must watch for any railfan who grew up with Conrail or its precursors in their back yard.
Love the vintage films and simple yet on the point narration.  This is for the hardcore train fan.  Excellent Video.
